<p class="MsoNormal">Hi Mansi Jagtap,<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">I trust this message finds you in good health. We want to express our heartfelt gratitude for your committed efforts and diligent work during your Training period at Vkraft Software Services Pvt Ltd. Commencing from December 1, 2023, you
 will be on a six-month probationary period.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">We are pleased to inform you that, based on your performance and contributions to the team, informed that your employment is being confirmed as Junior Software Engineer.
<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Your continued commitment to excellence has not gone unnoticed, and we are confident that you will continue to make valuable contributions to our organization. We believe that your skills and dedication will play a crucial role in the continued
 success of our team.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">Once again, congratulations on this achievement, and we look forward to your continued success as a member of the Vkraft family.<o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
